Colombia Recall Asprilla for First Post-World Cup Game
BOGOTA , December 23 ( Xinhua ) -- Colombia 's Faustino Asprilla was recalled to the national soccer team on Wednesday .
Asprilla was among 20 players named for the international friendly match at home to Denmark in January , Colombia 's first game since the World Cup finals , their first under new coach Javier Alvarez and their first since the international retirement of Carlos Valderrama .
Parma 's Asprilla was sent home after Colombia 's first World Cup match in France for publicly criticising coach Hernan Dario Gomez , who resigned after the competition , and other members of the squad .
